<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(الْمَسْأَلَة الْخَامِسَة وَالْعشْرُونَ)</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>: طلب المَاء قبل التَّيَمُّم <span class="c2">(كه)</span> :<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">الْمَذْهَب:</span> وَاجِب.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">عِنْدهم:</span> لَا يجب إِلَّا فِي مظانه.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">الدَّلِيل من الْمَنْقُول:</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">لنا:</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>الْآيَة.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>إِنَّمَا يعد عادما بعد الطّلب،<span class="c5"> فَفِي الشَّاهِد لَو قلت لصاحبك:</span> ابتع لي كَذَا، فَإِن لم تَجِد فَكَذَا لم يجز شِرَاء الثَّانِي إِلَّا بعد طلب الأول وفوته.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">لَهُم:</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">قَوْله عَلَيْهِ السَّلَام:</span> <span class="c1">" وترابها طهُورا "</span> سَمَّاهُ طهُورا، وَلم يشْتَرط الطّلب.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c5">الدَّلِيل من الْمَعْقُول:</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c5">لنا:</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>التَّيَمُّم مَشْرُوط بِعَدَمِ المَاء، وَلَا يعلم الْعَدَم إِلَّا بعد الطّلب؛ لِأَنَّهُ إِن<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>